So let's figure out the
slopes in each of these lines.

00:02:14.910 --> 00:02:16.810
I'll first do this one in pink.

00:02:16.810 --> 00:02:19.640
So this slope right here, so line one.

00:02:19.640 --> 00:02:21.920
So I'll call it slope one.

00:02:21.920 --> 00:02:25.130
Slope one is, let's just say it is,

00:02:25.130 --> 00:02:26.730
well I'll take this as
the finishing point,

00:02:26.730 --> 00:02:31.130
so negative three minus
zero, remember change in Y,

00:02:31.130 --> 00:02:35.263
negative three minus zero, over four,

00:02:37.040 --> 00:02:39.720
minus negative eight.

00:02:39.720 --> 00:02:41.240
Four minus negative eight,

00:02:41.240 --> 00:02:43.890
so this is equal to negative three,

00:02:43.890 --> 00:02:46.860
over, this is the same
thing as four plus eight,

00:02:46.860 --> 00:02:51.860
negative three over 12, which
is equal to negative 1/4.

00:02:52.340 --> 00:02:55.860
Divide the numerator by
the denominator by three,

00:02:55.860 --> 00:02:57.870
that's this line, the first line.

00:02:57.870 --> 00:02:59.800
Now what about the second line?

00:02:59.800 --> 00:03:03.630
The second line, the slope
for that second line is,

00:03:03.630 --> 00:03:06.740
well let's take, here negative one,

00:03:06.740 --> 00:03:10.197
negative one minus six, over negative one,

00:03:12.198 --> 00:03:16.615
minus negative two is equal
to negative one minus six

00:03:19.700 --> 00:03:24.586
is negative seven, over
negative one minus negative two,

00:03:24.586 --> 00:03:26.920
that's the same thing as
negative one plus two,

00:03:26.920 --> 00:03:28.430
well that's just one.

00:03:28.430 --> 00:03:32.460
So the slope here is negative seven.

00:03:32.460 --> 00:03:34.970
So here their slopes are neither equal,

00:03:34.970 --> 00:03:36.470
so they're not parallel.

00:03:36.470 --> 00:03:38.560
Nor are they the negative
inverse of each other,

00:03:38.560 --> 00:03:41.010
so this is neither, so
this is neither parallel

00:03:41.010 --> 00:03:43.410
or perpendicular.

00:03:43.410 --> 00:03:45.490
Neither parallel nor perpendicular,

00:03:45.490 --> 00:03:48.070
